Package de.oth.blocklib.world.chunks

This package contains everything that is needed to create the infinite world around the camera.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Chunk
    A Chunk, represented as a array of BlockType.
    ChunkCreatorCallable
    A Callable which is used to generate Chunks in a Thread, separate from the Main-Thread to prevent the main thread from freezing when new Chunks have to be loaded.
    ChunkLoadAndSaver
    This class uses the FileInputStream and the FileOutputStream to load and Save Chunks.
    ChunkManager
    The ChunkManager is used to manage a chunkArray which represents the Field of ChunkIDObjects around the camera.
    ChunkMesherCallable
    A Callable which is used to generate chunk meshes in a Thread, separate from the Main-Thread to prevent the main thread from freezing when new Chunks have to be loaded.
    ChunkSaverRunnable  
    ChunkStorage
    The ChunkStorage holds and manages all Chunks that are currently needed in any way.
    DistantChunkContainer
    A container that can hold a Chunk and a squared distance.
    OwnedChunk
    A simple class that is used by the ChunkStorage.
    OwnedFutureChunk
    A simple class, which is used by the ChunkStorage.
